To install the extension, you need to open the “Extensions” - “Manage Extensions” section in the Chrome browser or any other browser that uses the Chrome engine. 
Next, enable developer mode (top right). 
Then click the “Load unpacked extension” button. You will be asked to select a folder, select the one where you uploaded the extension files.
After confirmation, you will see the “Galxe Clicker” extension in the list of all extensions that you have, you will need to pin it.
When everything is ready, just go to any Galxe quest and after browsing the page, click on the “Galxe Clicker” icon of the extension. 
After waiting 5 seconds you can reload the page and the twitter/pages quests will be completed, if not, try reloading the page again, Galxe often lags.
